{"tid":2232564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文革?】工聯會設熱線　籲舉報「不良教材」「不當教學」","createTime":"2020-10-06T12:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T22:45:12.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f7bb1b461b0e8784e6cb6f8eb74708a700709f0f","tid":2232564,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/120753270_1303220830017650_7657189465271629750_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=0o_3_15BHdUAX-EF6l3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=d15ac0c33e2b0422eab4d9a65f5eede4&amp;oe=5FA2325B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F120753270_1303220830017650_7657189465271629750_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D0o_3_15BHdUAX-EF6l3%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26tp%3D7%26oh%3Dd15ac0c33e2b0422eab4d9a65f5eede4%26oe%3D5FA2325B&h=45496f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n教育局取消九龍塘宣道小學一名教師的註冊資格，指其在課程設計中散播「港獨」資訊；工聯會設立熱線，呼籲舉報「不良教材」或「不當教學行為」。<br />\n工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄在 FB 發文，標題為「愛護孩子&middot; 由您做起」，並附有工聯會的海報，指學生在校園努力學習，「絕不應受到不良教材或不當教學行為所影響」，工聯會會長吳秋北﹑立法會議員麥美娟和陸頌雄等，促請各界「全面監察坊間」學習教材，並設有報料專線，檢舉不良教材及不當教學行為。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/文革-工聯會設熱線-籲舉報-不良教材-不當教學/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%87%E9%9D%A9-%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%AD%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%9A-%E7%B1%B2%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90-%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=b01823c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%96%87%E9%9D%A9-%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%AD%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%9A-%E7%B1%B2%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90-%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%2F&h=3cb00c3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www